text: Fruitland may refer to: *Fruitland, California *Fruitland, Georgia *Fruitland, Idaho *Fruitland, Iowa *Fruitland, Maryland *Fruitland, Missouri *Fruitland, New Mexico *Fruitland Township, Michigan *Fruitland, Utah "Fruitland" is also a part of the name of: *Fruitland Park, Florida *Upper Fruitland, New Mexico *Fruitland formation, geological deposit in New Mexico and Colorado
